data.name: AboutLabel.Text
data.value: EndlessFire is an indie First-Person Shooter game/FPS game(semi-survival,lowpoly and ofiline/singleplayer), created by one person with UnityEngine.ln this game you are a soldier who has to do different special missions. You will complete these missions with the help of items and weapons that you will find on the map. During the missions you will encounter enemies who want to kill you. For this reason you will have to defend yourself with the weapons you will find in the game.
